graph LR
    Notebooks[Notebooks<br/>Workbench Images]

    %% External Dependencies - Required
    Notebooks -->|base image| UBI9[Red Hat UBI9<br/>Required]
    Notebooks -->|runtime| Python[Python 3.9/3.11<br/>Required]
    Notebooks -->|IDE| JupyterLab[JupyterLab 3.x/4.2<br/>Required]
    Notebooks -->|pipeline| Elyra[Elyra 3.x-4.x<br/>Required]
    Notebooks -->|CLI| OpenShiftClient[OpenShift Client oc<br/>Required]
    Notebooks -->|data| Pandas[Pandas<br/>Required]
    Notebooks -->|compute| NumPy[NumPy<br/>Required]
    Notebooks -->|ML| ScikitLearn[scikit-learn<br/>Required]
    Notebooks -->|viz| Matplotlib[Matplotlib<br/>Required]

    %% External Dependencies - Optional
    Notebooks -.->|DL framework| PyTorch[PyTorch 2.x<br/>Optional]
    Notebooks -.->|DL framework| TensorFlow[TensorFlow 2.x<br/>Optional]
    Notebooks -.->|GPU accel| CUDA[NVIDIA CUDA 11.8/12.x<br/>Optional]
    Notebooks -.->|GPU accel| ROCm[AMD ROCm 5.x/6.x<br/>Optional]
    Notebooks -.->|GPU accel| IntelOneAPI[Intel oneAPI<br/>Optional]
    Notebooks -.->|GPU accel| HabanaSDK[Habana SDK<br/>Optional]
    Notebooks -.->|IDE| CodeServer[Code Server 4.x<br/>Optional]
    Notebooks -.->|IDE| RStudioServer[RStudio Server<br/>Optional]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    Notebooks -->|lifecycle mgmt| NotebookController[ODH Notebook Controller<br/>Internal ODH]
    Notebooks -->|discovery| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Internal ODH]
    Notebooks -->|auth| OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>Internal ODH]
    Notebooks -->|image pull| ImageRegistry[OpenShift Image Registry<br/>Internal ODH]
    Notebooks -->|pipeline exec| ElyraService[Elyra Pipeline Service<br/>Internal ODH]
    Notebooks -.->|model storage| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Internal ODH]
    Notebooks -.->|pipeline tasks| DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Internal ODH]

    %% External Services
    Notebooks -->|package install| PyPI[PyPI pypi.org<br/>External Service]
    Notebooks -->|image registry| QuayIO[Quay.io<br/>External Service]
    Notebooks -->|packages| CDNRedHat[cdn.redhat.com<br/>External Service]
    Notebooks -->|data storage| S3Storage[S3 Storage<br/>External Service]
    Notebooks -->|version control| GitServers[GitHub/GitLab<br/>External Service]
    Notebooks -->|cluster API| K8sAPI[OpenShift API<br/>Cluster Service]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|reads annotations| Notebooks
    NotebookController -->|creates pods with| Notebooks
    DSPipelines -->|runs tasks| Notebooks
    ElyraService -->|executes runtime| Notebooks

